{
  "stem": "1132.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "One life was in school, and the other life was outside of school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "To bring in a Jewish story, I must've been, I think, a sophomore in high school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it was Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I was fasting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And this lady-- but nobody was supposed to know that I was in school on Yom Kippur fasting.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this lady-- I, I actually remember this-- who was a half Jew and knew very well that this was Yom Kippur-- I was standing in a corner talking to my friends.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she came around and said where's your lunch, knowing very well where my lunch was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said, I didn't see you in the lunch room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, I wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said to me, you're not eating because it's a Jewish holiday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, what if I'm not?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she says, there's not supposed to be any religious observation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have very clear memories of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I really think I bring a very mixed-up kind of a background to everything that I have ended up doing and being.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, what else do I remember?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember in '52 my father was no longer able to maintain a private law practice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So somewhere in '53 or so, he joined a newly formed cooperative, which could be viewed as a law firm, which is what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A whole bunch of lawyers were getting together and forming a cooperative, hoping that as a group, they were all going to make a living, and they were all going to survive.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember him going from a private, single attorney into this group practice, which totally changed everybody's life around.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I remember that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
